title: 08/17/21 DPS Hour 2 Sam Monson
itunes:title: 08/17/21 DPS Hour 2 Sam Monson
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Jason McIntyre, filling in for Dan, react to Tim Tebow being cut by the Jaguars after week 1 of the preseason and wonder if putting himself out there looked foolish. Sam Monson from ProFootballFocus gives him impressions on rookie QB's including an impressive debut from Zach Wilson. Plus, Joel Embiid banked in big time after repping himself.
